7) Alt + g - below lin 102 or under } paste:
$i++;
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['host']          = '__FILL_IN_DETAILS__';
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['port']          = '3306';
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['socket']        = '';
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['connect_type']  = 'tcp';
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['extension']     = 'mysql';
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['compress']      = FALSE;
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['auth_type']     = 'config';
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['user']          = '__FILL_IN_DETAILS__';
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['password']      = '__FILL_IN_DETAILS__'

Change FILL in DETAILS lines
host - endpoint url of data base , find on aws page
user - name of database
view credential details for host and user
password - enter password from before

